    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly and dependable daily driver? This vehicle is ready to get you where you need to go! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It's been a trusty companion and is looking for its next practical owner!",
